BeagleBone Black Custom Image Layer
====================================

This layer provides a custom image for BeagleBone Black with:
- UART console (ttyS0) support
- USB Ethernet gadget with DHCP server

Features:
---------
1. UART Console: Serial console on ttyS0 at 115200 baud
2. USB Ethernet: USB gadget mode with DHCP server
   - BeagleBone IP: 192.168.7.2
   - Client IP range: 192.168.7.1 (single IP)
   - DNS server: 192.168.7.2
3. SSH Server: OpenSSH server enabled with root login
   - SSH access: ssh root@192.168.7.2
   - Root login allowed (no password by default)

Usage:
------
1. Add this layer to bblayers.conf:
   /path/to/meta-bbb-custom

2. Build the image:
   bitbake beaglebone-black-image

3. Flash to SD card and boot

Dependencies:
-------------
- meta
- meta-poky
- meta-yocto-bsp (or meta-ti for BeagleBone support)
- meta-openembedded/meta-networking (for dnsmasq)

